Sudan announces its timetable for January's referendum on independence for the south, with 14 November named as the first date for voter registration. (BBC) (AFP via The Sydney Morning Herald)China's Vice President Xi Jinping is named vice-chair of the Central Military Commission. (BBC) (Xinhua) (CBC)The Obama administration notifies the United States Congress of plans for a $60billion-dollar weapons deal with Saudi Arabia in a move to threaten Iran. (CNN) (Reuters)